Class DistinctLabelIndex<T extends Label>

  • edu.umn.nlpengine.DistinctLabelIndex<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LabelIndex<T>

    public class DistinctLabelIndex<T extends Label>
implements LabelIndex<T>

    A label index where the labels are distinct i.e. non-overlapping.
